<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-justify">美酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还未煮开</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">岁月</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">从老照片里回头</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">扯一缕白发握在手心</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">把笔直的嵴背</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">弯成弓的模样</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">原来</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">季节和人</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一向藏着</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">三分醉和七分醒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201111/80f5234c69fc4db59d9e90fe6901498b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>冬日暖阳 草根一一</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">太阳出来</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每一道光都在奔跑</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">路过每一棵树每一株草</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每一条河都在燃烧</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">老家的空坝子</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">该是大衣棉被出场</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">晒一晒各自的家当</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">留住谁的目光</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">城里的公园广场</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">老人小孩过节似的</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">推开门走进阳光</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">散步跳舞写诗歌唱</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">阳光不贵</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不拒绝谁</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">冬日暖阳</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不忍心浪费</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">来源：匠心读书会微信公众号</p>
➜诗歌：丽江手札| 童光辉（四川邻水）
http://www.sohu.com/a/431132126_483111	32121
